            </a>
          </div>
        </section>
      </deific-home>
      <deific-about class="page">
        <div class="about">
          <img src="/assets/hasanirogers.webp" alt="Hasani Rogers, owner of Deific Arts, LLC">
          <div>
            <h2>I BUILD</h2>
            <deific-builds></deific-builds>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="find">
          <h3>Find me on the web:</h3>
          <ul>
            <li><a href="https://linktr.ee/deificarts">Link Tree</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://github.com/Deific-Arts">GitHub</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.facebook.com/deificartsllc">Facebook</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.threads.com/@deificarts">Threads</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.linkedin.com/company/deificarts">LinkedIn</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://youtube.com/@DeificArtsLLC">YouTube</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://bsky.app/profile/deificartsllc.bsky.social">Blue Sky</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://www.instagram.com/deificarts">Instagram</a></li>
            <li><a href="https://play.google.com/store/apps/dev?id=6851515481249949579&hl=en_US">Google Play</a></li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </deific-about>
      <deific-services class="page">Services</deific-services>
      <deific-work>
        <div slot="slide-0">
          <h2>Doctor at my Door</h2>
          <img src="/assets/damd-1280x720.webp" alt="Doctor at my Door" />
          <p>A custom WordPress site I built.</p>
        </div>
        <div slot="slide-1">
          <h2>Bob Cards</h2>
          <img src="/assets/bob-1280x720.webp" alt="Bob Cards" />
          <p>A headless WordPress implementation that uses FourSquare API for location data on black owned businesses.</p>
        </div>
        <div slot="slide-2">
          <h2>Garden's Care</h2>
          <img src="/assets/gardenscare-1280x720.webp" alt="Garden's Care" />
          <p>Another custom WordPress site I built.</p>
        </div>
        <div slot="slide-3">
          <h2>Ani Book Quotes</h2>
          <img src="/assets/ani-1280x720.webp" alt="Doctor at my Door" />
          <p>An app for book lovers built with Astro, Web Components, and Supabase.</p>
        </div>
        <div slot="slide-4">
          <h2>Kitely Tech</h2>
          <img src="/assets/kitely-1280x720.webp" alt="Kitely Tech" />
          <p>A company I partner with to provide web development services.</p>
        </div>
        <div slot="slide-5">
          <h2>Krafty Tarot</h2>
          <img src="/assets/krafty-1280x720.webp" alt="Krafty Tarot" />
          <p>A Wordpress tarot site I did for a Detroit based psychic.</p>
        </div>
      </deific-work>
      <LatestBlogPosts />
      <div style="height: 33vh;"></div>
      <deific-consultation url="https://calendly.com/contact-deificarts/consultation" class="page"></deific-consultation>
      <Footer />
    </main>
    <script src="https://unpkg.com/snapsvg@0.5.1/dist/snap.svg-min.js" defer></script>
    <script>
      // elements
      import '../elements/button';
      import '../elements/waves';
      import '../elements/services';
      import '../elements/work';
      import '../elements/consultation';
      // scripts
      import '../scripts/home';
    </script>
    <style>
      main {
        scroll-snap-type: y mandatory;
        scroll-behavior: smooth;
        height: 100vh;
        position: relative;
        z-index: 1;
        overflow-y: auto;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      deific-home {
        flex-direction: column;
      }

      deific-about {
        h2 {
          font-size: 2rem;
          opacity: 0.5;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          letter-spacing: 2px;
        }

        img {
          width: 150px;
          height: 150px;
          border-radius: 50%;
          object-fit: cover;
        }

        deific-builds {
          display: block;
          font-size: 3rem;
          font-weight: bold;
          text-transform: uppercase;
          line-height: 1.1;
          opacity: 1;
          text-align: left;
        }
        .Typewriter__cursor {
          color: var(--color-primary);
        }
      }

      deific-work {
        scroll-snap-align: start;
        [slot] {
          text-align: right;
          align-items: flex-end;
          position: relative;
          top: -10vh;
          padding: 2rem;
        }

        p, img {
          width: 100%;
          max-width: 66vw;
          text-align: right;
        }
      }

      deific-consultation {
        z-index: 999;
        @media screen and (width > 768px) {
          z-index: 1;
        }
      }

      .page {
        display: flex;
        padding: 1rem;
        width: 100%;
        height: calc(100vh - 230px);
        scroll-snap-align: start;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;

        & > * {
          width: 100%;
          height: 100%;
          margin: auto;
          display: flex;
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;

          @media (min-width: 1024px) {
            padding: 2rem;
          }
        }

        h2 {
          font-size: clamp(1rem, 5vw, 2rem);
          white-space: nowrap;
          margin-bottom: 1rem;

          span {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.5em;
            opacity: 0.5;
          }
        }

        .about {
          flex-direction: row;
          justify-content: flex-start;
          align-items: center;
          gap: 1.5rem;

          width: 100%;
          font-size: 2rem;
          text-align: left;
          flex-direction: column;
          justify-content: center;

          @media screen and (min-width: 769px) {
            flex-direction: row;
            justify-content: flex-start
          }
        }

        .featured {
          text-align: left;
          align-items: center;
          justify-content: center;
          gap: 2rem;
          max-width: 960px;
          margin: auto;
          padding: 0 2rem;

          img {
            display: none;
            @media (width > 768px) {
              display: block;
            }
          }


          @media (width > 768px) {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: 3fr 2fr;
          }
        }
      }

      deific-about.page {
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: flex-start;
        justify-content: flex-start;

        ul {
          display: flex;
          gap: 1rem;
          list-style: none;
          margin: 0;
          padding: 0;
          flex-wrap: wrap;
        }

        .find {
          flex-direction: column;
          align-items: flex-start;
          justify-content: flex-start;
        }
      }

      #logo {
        width: 66%;
        max-width: 640px;
        opacity: 0;
        animation:
          drop-in 1000ms ease-out forwards,
          fade-in 2000ms ease-out forwards;
      }
    </style>
  </body>
</html>
